title: Roy Eldridge with Gene Krupa feat. Anita O'Day (1941-49)
description:

All tracks by Gene Krupa & His Orchestra
All tracks feature Roy Eldridge on trumpet (some on vocals)
Many tracks feature Anita O'Day on vocals
The last four tracks feature Delores Hawkins on vocals

Tracks 1-20 recorded between May 8, 1941 and July 13, 1942
Tracks 21-24 recorded Jan 26 & May 9, 1949
